  • java.lang.Object

    PlusStationFactory, StandardStationFactory
    public abstract class AbstractStationFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements Observable, java.io.Serializable

    AbstractStationFactory

    This class is an abstract model for the Factory station which parks bikes and interact with users.
